<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Welcome to Fake Fortuny</title>
    <style type="text/css">
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            height: 100vh;
            min-width: 100%;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            color: #222222;
        }

        a {
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
            line-height: 1.25;
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .status {
            color: #fff;
            width: 100px;
            padding: 10px;
            animation: blink 2s infinite;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        @keyframes blink {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
            }

            to {
                opacity: 1;
            }
        }

        p {
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }

        .divider {
            border-top: 1px solid #ccc;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .email-wrapper {
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .email-header {
            background-color: #1e1e1e;
            padding: 30px;
            color: #f086d9;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .email-body {
            padding: 14px;
            background-color: #f4f3f3;
            height: 70vh;
        }

        .email-footer {
            background-color: #1e1e1e;
            padding: 14px;
            color: #F8F8F8;
            text-align: center;
        }

        img {
        padding: 24px;
        max-width: 200px; /* Set max-width to control size */
        height: auto; /* Maintain aspect ratio */
        display: block; /* Ensure centering */
        margin: 0 auto; /* Center horizontally */
        object-fit: contain; /* Prevent stretching */
        filter: invert(100%); /* Maintain white color effect */
      }

      /* Mobile-specific adjustments */
      @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
        .email-header {
          padding: 15px; /* Reduce padding on mobile */
        }

        img {
          padding: 10px; /* Reduce image padding on mobile */
          max-width: 150px; /* Smaller size for mobile */
          height: auto;
          margin: 0 auto; /* Ensure centering */
        }

        .email-body {
          height: auto; /* Allow flexible height on mobile */
          padding: 10px;
        }
      }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="email-wrapper">
        <div class="email-header">
            <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dq4a3jp66/image/upload/v1754225482/light__tvaq2z.png"
                height="200px" width="200px" alt="Fortuny Logo">
        </div>
        <div class="email-body">
            <p>Hello <%= name %>,</p>
            <p>Welcome to Fortuny, where timeless elegance meets exquisite craftsmanship. We are delighted to have you
                join our community of discerning individuals who appreciate the art of fine fabrics and lighting.</p>
            <p>Explore our collections, inspired by the rich heritage of Mariano Fortuny, and discover products that
                bring sophistication and beauty to your spaces.</p>
            <p>Stay connected for exclusive updates, design inspirations, and special offers tailored just for you.</p>
            <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please <a href="https://www.fortuny.com/contact/">contact
                    us</a>.</p>
            <p>Thank you for choosing Fortuny. Letâ€™s create something beautiful together!</p>
        </div>
        <div class="email-footer">
            <p>&copy;
                <script>document.write(new Date().getFullYear())</script> Fortuny. All rights reserved.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>